What you need to know:

Calvert-Lewin opened the scoring at Wembley with his 10th goal this season after netting nine times in six games for Everton.The 23-year-old's first half strike was followed by another maiden England goal as Wolves defender Conor Coady struck after the interval.On his first England start, Southampton striker Danny Ings got the third goal -- his first for his country -- with a fine overhead kick.